System architecture
System = Cpu + operating System
# OS operating system
= OSX , Linux , Widows  -> special kind of sw which take advantage of hardware capabilities and expose them to 3rd party application
in conviennent and performant way

------------------------------------------
# 1 Single - Tasking system
= Execute the machine code of one single task until task terminates
= os can only run on program at time and in order to run another you need to fully close first

------------------------------------------
Example on OS that was single : MD
